3.00	Charge_It_2_da_Game	Charge It 2 da Game	Charge It 2 Da Game is the second studio album by American rapper Silkk The Shocker, released February 17, 1998 on No Limit Records. Charge It 2 Da Game debuted at #3 on the Billboard 200 and #1 on the Top R&amp;B/Hip-Hop Albums. Two charting singles were released from the album, "Just Be Straight with Me" (featuring Master P and Destiny's Child), and "It Ain't My Fault" (featuring Mystikal). Charge It 2 Da Game received and official Platinum certification by the Recording Industry Association of America on March 25, 1998.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/b/b7/ChargeIt2DaGame98.jpg/220px-ChargeIt2DaGame98.jpg
